      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence model was selected based on prior literature for rotating machinery. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was adopted without systematic comparison to alternative constitutive models (e.g., Taskin, Faghih-Sharp). Model form uncertainty is not formally propagated through the Monte Carlo UQ."
